3(f) Special Business - City Canterbury Council

Location:
Lakemba is a suburb in south-western Sydney located 15 kilometres south-west of the Sydney central business district, in the local government area of the City of Canterbury.

Description:
The property comprises of a modern 3 storey commercial building with a basement car park which is accessed via the rear lane, Baden Powell Place.

The Ground Floor: (vacant)
The ground floor is suited for wholesaler or manufacturer as there is a showroom, workshop and goods lift to the basement car park.

The First Floor: (partially leased)
The first floor is suited to suburban office use. The space has been divided into 4 separate tenancies which of one is currently leased.

The Second Floor: (vacant)
The second floor was previously used as a reception centre which has a modern and functional layout. This space would also suit a number of alternative uses.

Tenancies:
One suite on the first floor plus part of the rooftop (currently leased to Optus) is returning $41,485 per annum.

CBRE & I.B Property, as exclusive selling agents, are delighted to present for sale, 194-198 Lakemba St, Lakemba; a three level commercial building which has recently been refurbished over basement carparking within walking distance to Lakemba Railway Station & Lakemba Shopping Centre.

Commanding a prominent corner location in the heart of Lakemba with an extensive frontage to Lakemba St & Croydon St, this freestanding commercial building which was built in the 1990’s consists of two commercial floors and secure basement car parking for 64 cars will be one of the most sought after in 2021.

Location: Located on the Eastern side of Lakemba St. Lakemba is a major inner west growth suburb within Metropolitan Sydney. 260m walking distance to Lakemba Railway Station.
25 kms* west of Sydney CBD and 18 kms* south-east of Parramatta CBD. Close vicinity to all essential amenity.

The property will attract several buyers because of its many key attributes, including:
*Net Lettable Area: 2,294sqm*
*Zoned B2 Local Centre
*4 Star NABERS Energy Rating
*Ideal for owner occupiers, investors & developers
* New Metro line being built between Bankstown - Sydenham
